 of 10^11 M_\\odot.\nThis result corroborates the possible link between the QSO activity and the\nformation of massive spheroids.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Oct 2004 13:12:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
