ime-domain\nmultiplexer (MUX). We give an overview of the SCUBA-2 system and an update on\nits status, and describe some of the technological innovations that make this\nunique instrument possible.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Oct 2004 14:47:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-26"}
